DarkMouse::

She finished studying the layout and weapons programs.  She noticed 
that several programs and files were encrypted and locked behind 
passwords that would take her a while to figure out. And with 
Galvatron practically over her shoulder, she wasn't about to get on 
his bad side. Still, her almost uncontrolable curiosity was nagging 
at her. What secrets is he hiding, she wondered. 

She finishes  down loading all the info she could and sat back in the 
comm chair.  She noticed on the monitor that there was a sizable 
amount of comm transmissions going on. "Hey, Galv, what's with all 
this? You'd think there was a convention going on. What do you make 
of it?" as she motioned for him to check out the monitor.
